{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9dcb35be53","title":"中央关于召开各区负责同志会议讨论军事、土改等问题的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"35d435db67","index":0,"year":1950,"month":3,"day":18,"articleId":"9dcb35be53"}],"tags":[{"id":"af71a4eedb","name":"高岗","type":"人物"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"3accd37c83","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9dcb35be53","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"德怀，即彭德怀，当时任中共中央西北局第一书记。小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央西南局第一书记。激石，即饶激石，当时任中共中央华东局第一书记。方方，当时任中共中央华南分局第三书记。高岗，当时任中共中央东北局书记。"},{"id":"bebb460e7b","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9dcb35be53","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林彪，当时任中共中央中南局第一书记。票裕，当时任中国人民解放军第三野战军副司令员、华东军区副司令员。"},{"id":"fc5e41e30d","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9dcb35be53","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"剑英，即叶剑英，当时任中共中央华南分局第一书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"32a279cb7b","type":"title","text":"中央关于召开各区负责同志会议讨论军事、土改等问题的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9dcb35be53"},{"id":"3accd37c83","type":"paragraph","text":"德怀、小平、激石、方方、高岗\"同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9dcb35be53"},{"id":"bebb460e7b","type":"paragraph","text":"为讨论军事和土改等项问题，拟请各区负责同志来京开会一次，请你们五位于接电后数日内即动身来京（林彪栗裕二同志已到京）。为此，西北军区会议须改期开会。彭来京用何交通工具望告，我们意见可乘火车。小平何日动身为宜望告确期，以便派飞机来接。剑英刚从武汉回粤，请方方来京一次。彭邓饶方四同志可于三月廿四、五两日到京，高岗同志到京时间另电通知","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9dcb35be53"},{"id":"fc5e41e30d","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9dcb35be53"},{"id":"abafc105f6","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十八日上午一时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9dcb35be53"}],"page":{"id":"61e2f38d40","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"9dcb35be53","start":244,"end":244}}}},"__N_SSG":true}